8 PC 3/8 Inch Drive Triple Square Driver Bit Set

  • Bit sockets are 3/8" sq
  • dr
  • with a black oxide tip, matte finish and made from SNCM 8660 steel
  • For use on triple square fastener bolts typically found on European vehicles (especially German)
  • For use on cylinder heads, axle shafts, rear toe adjusters, differentials, transmission drain plugs, clutches, belly pans, brake calipers and more
  • Other uses include: Detroit Diesel flywheel bolts, crank pullers on 900 &4000 series engine, and headbolts on 900 series
